postgres-description =
    PostgreSQL is a powerful, open-source object-relational database system with over
    35 years of active development.

    It is the recommended backing store for most FreeSynergy container apps, including
    Forgejo, Outline, Pretix, and Vikunja. PostgreSQL is ACID-compliant, highly
    extensible, and supports advanced data types, full-text search, and JSON.

postgres-features =
    - ACID-compliant transactions
    - Advanced data types (JSON, arrays, hstore, PostGIS)
    - Full-text search
    - Logical and physical replication
    - Row-level security
    - Extensible with custom functions and types
